Like, who's the worst?

01:43.228 --> 01:45.314
I really don't want
to do this, okay?

01:45.314 --> 01:47.441
I-I mean, I used to do stuff
like this all the time,

01:47.441 --> 01:49.109
but now I just want to work.

01:49.109 --> 01:50.402
- So...
- Come on, I got no one

01:50.402 --> 01:52.029
to talk to about this stuff.

01:52.029 --> 01:53.947
What about Aaron in sales?
Like...

01:53.947 --> 01:55.282
- Come on.
- He's not annoying?

01:55.282 --> 01:56.616
Come on, you can't tell me
he's not.

01:56.616 --> 01:58.201
But he's cute;
he, like, dresses well,

01:58.201 --> 01:59.411
so he's got that going for him.

01:59.411 --> 02:02.122
