What about swank?

02:05.876 --> 02:07.085
- No.
- Foxy.

02:07.085 --> 02:09.129
- What?
- Looking foxy.

02:09.129 --> 02:11.256
- Ugh, don't say "foxy."
- What's wrong with that?

02:11.256 --> 02:13.425
Oh, come on, man.
What is guys' obsession

02:13.425 --> 02:15.302
with complimenting
the way people look?

02:15.302 --> 02:17.304
Like, what do you think
is gonna happen if you don't?

02:25.479 --> 02:27.898
Actually, you know what?
This is a hot take.

02:27.898 --> 02:29.691
- It is?
- Yes, this is like,

02:29.691 --> 02:32.486
is this the end of compliments
in the workplace?

02:32.486 --> 02:34.071
That's really good, Sam,

02:34.071 --> 02:35.614
- I want you to write that up.
- Okay.

02:35.614 --> 02:37.449
We'll call it
"Sam's Hot Takes."

02:37.449 --> 02:39.451
Cool, yeah, I-I would love that.

02:39.451 --> 02:40.994
You could just do
a regular thing.

02:40.994 --> 02:43.080
What if we call it this:

02:43.080 --> 02:45.040
"Sober Sam's Hot Takes"?

02:45.040 --> 02:47.626
It's your perspective,
it's your angle.

02:47.626 --> 02:50.128
Right. Yeah, no, let me, uh,
let me think about that.

02:50.128 --> 02:51.838
- Sleep on it, sleep on it.
- Okay, yeah.

02:51.838 --> 02:54.049
Ooh! "Sober Sam Sleeps On It."

02:54.049 --> 02:56.134
Yeah, okay.

02:56.134 --> 02:58.136
Picture your, like, bio, and
it's, like, a drawing of you,

02:58.136 --> 03:00.472
and you're, like,
chewing on your pen,

03:00.472 --> 03:02.140
and you're drooling
'cause you're sleeping,

03:02.140 --> 03:05.936
and then the drool becomes
the pen ink, right?

03:05.936 --> 03:07.688
Oh.

03:07.688 --> 03:09.815
♪ ♪

03:14.569 --> 03:17.698
<i>♪ So, you're looking
for the truth ♪</i>

03:18.824 --> 03:23.495
