for Guy's double-fried taquitos.

05:34.125 --> 05:36.294
And I'm gonna go now.

05:36.294 --> 05:38.046
Gah, get out!

05:38.046 --> 05:40.257
- He's already gone.
- (sighs)

05:40.257 --> 05:43.134
Okay, look, I'm--
I'm not gonna say

05:43.134 --> 05:45.178
that I'm glad
you were fired, but...

05:45.178 --> 05:48.348
Yeah, I'm not gonna say
I'm glad I got fired, either.

05:48.348 --> 05:51.017
That was really bad.
But this is a silver lining.

05:51.017 --> 05:53.812
I'm just really happy you said
you'd go on a date with me.

05:53.812 --> 05:55.605
