just gassing you up at work

05:58.191 --> 06:01.528
because I was into you,
because that's not the truth.

06:01.528 --> 06:03.405
I think you're
a really incredible writer.

06:03.405 --> 06:04.656
You could have told me

06:04.656 --> 06:05.699
that you were just doing
all of that

06:05.699 --> 06:06.908
'cause you thought I was hot.

06:06.908 --> 06:08.451
I think I might have
actually preferred it.

06:08.451 --> 06:10.537
You are hot, that's fact.

06:10.537 --> 06:14.040
But... you are also
a very gifted writer.

06:14.040 --> 06:16.167
- Okay, stop.
- You are.

06:16.167 --> 06:17.669
Why-why can't you take
a compliment?

06:17.669 --> 06:19.629
Sorry, you're right.
I'm sorry.

06:19.629 --> 06:22.465
Thank you for the compliment,
I really enjoyed it.

06:22.465 --> 06:25.176
All right, that was worse
than the first time.

06:25.176 --> 06:26.720
- (laughs)
- I hated that even more.

06:27.679 --> 06:29.264
I used to be just like you.

06:29.264 --> 06:30.765
I grew up poor in Queens

06:30.765 --> 06:32.851
and I never thought I should be
invited to the party.

06:32.851 --> 06:35.186
But truly,
there is no invitation.

06:35.186 --> 06:36.479
No one invited me
to go to college.

06:36.479 --> 06:37.814
I was the first
in my family to do it.

06:37.814 --> 06:40.442
I studied so hard, I didn't
get laid for four years.

06:40.442 --> 06:41.568
- Wow.
- Yeah.

06:41.568 --> 06:43.612
- That's impressive.
- Thank you.

06:43.612 --> 06:45.405
Did you see what I did there?

06:45.405 --> 06:46.948
- Yes, you sincerely
took the compliment.
- You complimented me.

06:46.948 --> 06:48.617
I took it, and it--
you felt good.

06:48.617 --> 06:50.577
- It was nice, yeah.
- (chuckles)

06:50.577 --> 06:52.621
- Sir. Madam.
- Yes.

06:52.621 --> 06:56.499
Here's your Biondi Santi
Brunello Di Montalcino.

06:56.499 --> 06:57.876
It's bold,
dry with a brightness,

06:57.876 --> 07:00.712
